# IMPORTANT: data/ files are committed on purpose.
# Do NOT add data/*.csv or data/*.json to this gitignore — those files ARE
# the thesis output, and the dashboard's contract with the thesis depends on
# them being version-controlled. The only data file that may be missing is
# data/per_container_r2.csv (1.4 MB) — that one IS committed once you copy
# it over from the thesis repo's results/alibaba/diagnostics/ folder.
